column52:
The public has been aware of Johnny Depp's marriage/divorce to Amber Heard, where Heard accused Depp of domestic violence & became a darling of the #MeToo Mvmt even though there was no proof & he had no history of violence with any previous partner & Heard had.

She became a Human Rights Champion of the United Nations Human Rights Office, was appointed ambassador on women's rights at the American Civil Liberties Union, and was hired by L'Oreal Paris as its global spokesperson

There is overwhelming evidence that she was the perpetrator of domestic violence against him all along as well as concocting an elaborate hoax to slander his name and to elevate her status and primarily to stretch her 15mins of fame/gain money. She took advantage of the mvmt to come out the victim when she completely victimized him.

Here's all the evidence against her (for a comprehensive view with documentation/proof watch these videos from youtuber "Autumn On Venus" provided below):

* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDAMV2
* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDAHV1
* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDAMV3
Exes Defending Him:
* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDXDefend
* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDXDefend2
More Including Audio:

* https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aca0KWoHtqQ

* https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eWijmDzZeJU&t=2s

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aca0KWoHtqQ
My observations, all in videos:
* She blackmailed him,
* She has a history of domestic violence whereas JD doesn't
* The police reported no marks/bruises on AH on the night of the alleged attack
* She never acted like a trauma victim: i.e immediately getting into another relationship, trying to get spousal support, dragging out the situation, not willing to sit down for a deposition, etc
* He on the other hand withdrew from public eye, started drinking again, became disheveled, etc
* He now has 87 surveillance cam footage & many witnesses
* She has a video begging him to come home when she feared for her life?
* Victims don't constantly talk about this, she can't stop
* 4,000 more pieces of evidence he submitted 

Blacklist this abuser, please!


Please Remove Amber Heard from any future DC property & as any spokesperson for domestic violence. Just as any man would under the same circumstances.

I started this petition because...
I believe in justice no matter who is the accuser/accused. If you do too, please sign

column52:
The public has been aware of Johnny Depp's marriage/divorce to Amber Heard, where Heard accused Depp of domestic violence & became a darling of the #MeToo Mvmt even though there was no proof & he had no history of violence with any previous partner & Heard had.

She became a Human Rights Champion of the United Nations Human Rights Office, was appointed ambassador on women's rights at the American Civil Liberties Union, and was hired by L'Oreal Paris as its global spokesperson

There is overwhelming evidence that she was the perpetrator of domestic violence against him all along as well as concocting an elaborate hoax to slander his name and to elevate her status and primarily to stretch her 15mins of fame/gain money. She took advantage of the mvmt to come out the victim when she completely victimized him.

Here's all the evidence against her (for a comprehensive view with documentation/proof watch these videos from youtuber "Autumn On Venus" provided below):

* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDAMV2
* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDAHV1
* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDAMV3
Exes Defending Him:
* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDXDefend
* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDXDefend2
More Including Audio:

* https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aca0KWoHtqQ

* https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eWijmDzZeJU&t=2s

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aca0KWoHtqQ
My observations, all in videos:
* She blackmailed him,
* She has a history of domestic violence whereas JD doesn't
* The police reported no marks/bruises on AH on the night of the alleged attack
* She never acted like a trauma victim: i.e immediately getting into another relationship, trying to get spousal support, dragging out the situation, not willing to sit down for a deposition, etc
* He on the other hand withdrew from public eye, started drinking again, became disheveled, etc
* He now has 87 surveillance cam footage & many witnesses
* She has a video begging him to come home when she feared for her life?
* Victims don't constantly talk about this, she can't stop
* 4,000 more pieces of evidence he submitted 

Blacklist this abuser, please!


Please Remove Amber Heard from any future DC property & as any spokesperson for domestic violence. Just as any man would under the same circumstances.

I believe in justice no matter who is the accuser/accused. If you do too, please sign

column52:
The public has been aware of Johnny Depp's marriage/divorce to Amber Heard, where Heard accused Depp of domestic violence & became a darling of the #MeToo Mvmt even though there was no proof & he had no history of violence with any previous partner & Heard had.

She became a Human Rights Champion of the United Nations Human Rights Office, was appointed ambassador on women's rights at the American Civil Liberties Union, and was hired by L'Oreal Paris as its global spokesperson

There is overwhelming evidence that she was the perpetrator of domestic violence against him all along as well as concocting an elaborate hoax to slander his name and to elevate her status and primarily to stretch her 15mins of fame/gain money. She took advantage of the mvmt to come out the victim when she completely victimized him.

Here's all the evidence against her (for a comprehensive view with documentation/proof watch these videos from youtuber "Autumn On Venus" provided below):

* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDAMV2
* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDAHV1
* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDAMV3
Exes Defending Him:
* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDXDefend
* https://www.tinyurl.com/JDXDefend2
More Including Audio:

* https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aca0KWoHtqQ

* https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eWijmDzZeJU&t=2s

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aca0KWoHtqQ
My observations, all in videos:
* She blackmailed him,
* She has a history of domestic violence whereas JD doesn't
* The police reported no marks/bruises on AH on the night of the alleged attack
* She never acted like a trauma victim: i.e immediately getting into another relationship, trying to get spousal support, dragging out the situation, not willing to sit down for a deposition, etc
* He on the other hand withdrew from public eye, started drinking again, became disheveled, etc
* He now has 87 surveillance cam footage & many witnesses
* She has a video begging him to come home when she feared for her life?
* Victims don't constantly talk about this, she can't stop
* 4,000 more pieces of evidence he submitted 

Blacklist this abuser, please!


Please Remove Amber Heard from any future DC property & as any spokesperson for domestic violence. Just as any man would under the same circumstances.

I started this petition because...
I believe in justice no matter who is the accuser/accused. If you do too, please sign
